{"tid":371416,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"別被騙了！專家：人體並沒有排毒時間表","createTime":"2017-08-23T16:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T04:36:48.000Z","uid":39971,"like":57,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c377ef0b0cc2ef23f1b147f231636fc29ed196e5","tid":371416,"uid":39971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:29:29.000Z","msg":"真的存在「人體排毒時間表」嗎？<br />\n<br />\n晚上9點至11點要保證身體處於安靜狀態，這樣淋巴才能好好排毒；<br />\n<br />\n晚上11點至凌晨1點間一定要處於熟睡狀態，這樣肝臟才能排毒；<br />\n<br />\n排便要在早上7點之前，因為這是大腸排毒的時間&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n相信很多人都在網上看到過這樣的說法，那麼，「人體排毒時間表」真的具有科學性嗎？<br />\n<br />\n專家稱，人體並沒有排毒時間表！<br />\n<br />\n每個人都有自己的生物鐘，而某個器官在特定時間段進行排毒的說法很牽強，<br />\n<br />\n因為人的代謝、排泄以及解毒的體系非常完善，根本無須刻意地去「按時排毒」。<br />\n<br />\n不吸菸、不喝酒、不吃高糖和油炸食品等，就能減輕排毒負擔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://history.people.com.cn/yangsheng/BIG5/n/2014/0403/c375422-24819106.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhistory.people.com.cn%2Fyangsheng%2FBIG5%2Fn%2F2014%2F0403%2Fc375422-24819106.html&d=t8RNb9JQXP%2Fjt%2Bh41aS3CPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=9189ec9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://history.people.com.cn/yangsheng/BIG5/n/2014/0403/c375422-24819106.html</a><br />\n<br />\n以後唔撚洗瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0adf58509a2fce9a3947c70f3e820eb77974d0","tid":371416,"uid":87428,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:35:59.000Z","msg":"好好笑  以前細個成日聽<br />\n晚晚唔到一點唔訓 <br />\n<br />\n利申：矮仔"},{"pid":"0b200f55f9b96bb24c2cb02a21514ac6969cbff4","tid":371416,"uid":39971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好好笑  以前細個成日聽<br />\n晚晚唔到一點唔訓 <br />\n<br />\n利申：矮仔</blockquote><br />\n基因問題定真係關夜瞓事？"},{"pid":"7a2a4f5d5526332dd36cc57b63a74f59baf18b41","tid":371416,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:02:52.000Z","msg":"有時差點計?"},{"pid":"45523d98f80b6aeff817a11199d36215b5b0d0bc","tid":371416,"uid":59886,"like":29